* How to install
just type, 

 sudo aptitude install eigen3-dev

or

http://eigen.tuxfamily.org/index.php?title=Main_Page~
Get the latest Eigen.~

 cd ~/Download/
 tar xvf eigen-eigen-***
 cd eigen-eigen-***
 mkdir build
 cd build
 cmake ..
 make 
 sudo make install

* Sample
 cd eigen
 g++ -I/usr/local/eigen3/ hallo.cpp 
